                            "380026"c., 88 42</li>
<li class="item">John Garrison, care of School-rooms, 77 00</li>
<li class="item">Proportion of fuel, "380026"c., charged to District, 81 00</li>
<li class="item">---$1277 12</li>
<li class="item">----</li>
<li class="item">Unexpended balance, $1437 49</li>
</ul></div>
<p>7</p>
<div class="p">
                    <span class="listhead"><em>District No.</em> 2.</span>
<ul><li class="item"> Balance in Treasury, March, 1856, $261 41</li>
